translation.Name: Rio Note - Moving
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: It has been nice living in Rio, but it is time I move to São Paulo. Almost everyone in my family lives there, I am one of the only ones in our family that lives around here, even my grandma lives in São Paulo!
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_1: I've also got some interesting job opportunities around there already, which means that I wont be jobless, that is good. There is even this security job which seens interesting, I've heard that they were paying very well for people who works in those facilities.
